<table class=pleasenote1><tr><td width=20>
<img src=tips.gif height=60></td><td>Quite often you cannot access a page because a message says that your browser does not allow cookies.  Don't be afraid to accept them if you really want to access the website.
<br /><i>This is what you have to do to enable cookies:</i>
